sentences: Narayanan Nair Harikumar (born 19 July 1955) is a sound editor, designer and mixing engineer, known for his works in Malayalam films.
N. Harikumar was born on 19 July 1955 in Kollam.
In 1979, he joined Chitranjali Studio as sound recordist under renowned sound engineer P. Devadas.
2014 -  My Life Partner and other films (Sound mixing)Other awards2005 - Kerala State Film Critics Award for Best Sound mixing - Oridam
2011 - John Abraham National Award Special Mention for Sound mixing
